It is a great guitar, better than my expectations and had heared good thing. I have access to the original maker G----n SG and surprised at how great this compares to it, plus has prettier inlays! A little tarnish on the gold hardware that is to be expected, see pictures, an almost inpercetable and unphotographable little dent in paint on back. A great demo of this model is found on Youtube by Pistol Pete. Would keep it but do not need it have dozens of guitars Comes with a soft gig bag. Great Christmas present or find a poor young talent to give it forward to. PS- was lazy so some of pictures are from the original auction.
